    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Enrich contact records with HubSpot and HTTP / REST API at scale for Routing (04585)\n\n**Pattern:** Data Enrichment · **Level:** Foundation · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nEnrich contact records with HubSpot and HTTP / REST API at scale for Routing (04585). It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual routing is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nDaily Schedule → Load Previous Snapshot → Fetch Changes Since Watermark → Normalize Records → Upsert into HubSpot → Advance Watermark → Persist Watermark (Notion) → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to data enrichment without manual effort\n- Anyone automating routing in sales\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Has retries and error handling built in\n- Removes copy-paste errors\n- Scales without extra headcount\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: API key / bearer for the target API; HubSpot private-app token; Notion integration token.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.",
        "width": 480,
        "height": 900
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
